Subject: [PATCH 5/5] =?UTF-8?q?Fix=20auto=20bus=20entry:=20handle=20postur?=
 =?UTF-8?q?e=3Dtrue=20case=20where=2045=C2=B0=20segment=20is=20not=20at=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?bus=20end?=
